Where'd you go, grandpa?

48:22.316 --> 48:24.239
Don't freak out, gravity face.

48:24.777 --> 48:26.495
Eat my dust, gray fangs!

48:26.695 --> 48:28.697
56 and 43, to my side.

48:32.159 --> 48:33.160
Whoo!

48:40.668 --> 48:43.012
Prepare to cry, Billy Backpack.

48:45.673 --> 48:48.517
That's how we do it!
Half-pipe, baby!

48:48.634 --> 48:50.511
Whatever.

48:53.013 --> 48:54.640
Yes. Keep smelling.

48:54.723 --> 48:59.820
You catch the human, and then
I will make human potpie!

49:02.189 --> 49:05.910
<font color="#808080">DRACULA:</font> 27, 45, 65, 76,
