49:06.235 --> 49:07.452
Block his path!

49:09.363 --> 49:10.410
<font color="#D900D9">(DRACULA LAUGHING)</font>

49:12.158 --> 49:13.375
Whoa-ho!

49:16.745 --> 49:18.713
Oh, come on now, dude man!

49:18.789 --> 49:20.336
Nice!

49:20.416 --> 49:21.463
<font color="#D900D9">(MURMURING)</font>

49:21.709 --> 49:24.258
Haha! Whoa-ho-ho!

49:28.090 --> 49:29.387
I got you, buddy.

49:32.136 --> 49:33.513
Do not disturb!

49:33.596 --> 49:34.939
People trying to sleep here!

